1
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:32,000
=Our Days=

2
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,720
(Adapted from Lang Lang's original novel
"The Prime of the Goddess")

3
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,160
=Episode 33=

4
00:01:38,562 --> 00:01:40,162
If we sleep vertically,

5
00:01:40,642 --> 00:01:41,881
I don't think we'll fit.

6
00:01:42,321 --> 00:01:43,121
It'll be too crowded.

7
00:01:44,082 --> 00:01:45,002
Let's sleep horizontally then.

8
00:01:45,041 --> 00:01:45,761
Yeah, horizontally.

9
00:01:46,481 --> 00:01:47,002
We'll sleep in a row.

10
00:01:47,321 --> 00:01:47,802
Alright.

11
00:01:49,041 --> 00:01:50,562
It's been a long time
since we slept together.

12
00:01:58,082 --> 00:01:58,601
Qian.

13
00:01:59,601 --> 00:02:00,362
Are we sleeping horizontally?

14
00:02:00,442 --> 00:02:01,041
Yes, horizontally.

15
00:02:01,481 --> 00:02:02,521
The bed can't fit us if we sleep
vertically. It'll be crowded too.

16
00:02:07,202 --> 00:02:08,002
I'll sleep inside.

17
00:02:08,082 --> 00:02:09,002
I'm turning off the light.

18
00:02:11,362 --> 00:02:12,121
Lie down.

19
00:02:14,962 --> 00:02:16,402
This makes me feel
like childhood again.

20
00:02:17,321 --> 00:02:18,481
It's always you
who turned off the light.

21
00:02:22,842 --> 00:02:23,761
Are you squeezed over there?

22
00:02:23,962 --> 00:02:25,562
No, there's plenty of space here.

23
00:02:26,122 --> 00:02:27,842
Back then, we only had two rooms.

24
00:02:27,842 --> 00:02:28,722
Once the light is switched off,

25
00:02:28,801 --> 00:02:30,402
both of you lose track of the bed.

26
00:02:32,722 --> 00:02:33,442
It's like, with the light off,

27
00:02:33,522 --> 00:02:34,601
it was impossible to find the bed.

28
00:02:35,201 --> 00:02:36,282
We just wanted to rely on you.

29
00:02:39,442 --> 00:02:40,201
I feel like

30
00:02:40,201 --> 00:02:41,761
my feet are outside the bed.

31
00:02:42,881 --> 00:02:43,962
Mine too.

32
00:02:44,522 --> 00:02:45,601
Is this bed a bit short?

33
00:02:46,321 --> 00:02:46,962
I...

34
00:02:48,361 --> 00:02:49,081
It fits me just fine.

35
00:02:50,201 --> 00:02:51,242
I'm short.

36
00:02:51,722 --> 00:02:52,881
I'm short.

37
00:02:53,481 --> 00:02:54,722
This seems perfect for you.

38
00:02:55,522 --> 00:02:56,442
You're right.

39
00:02:56,842 --> 00:02:58,761
This bed seems like it was
designed just for me.

40
00:02:59,682 --> 00:03:00,842
I'm sorry, Zhong.

41
00:03:01,242 --> 00:03:01,921
What's up?

42
00:03:02,682 --> 00:03:04,282
It seems you didn't drink
enough milk growing up.

43
00:03:04,722 --> 00:03:05,641
Hey you!

44
00:03:05,801 --> 00:03:07,002
You're mocking me.

45
00:03:07,921 --> 00:03:08,682
Your sister, Zhong

46
00:03:08,801 --> 00:03:10,321
ate all organic food,

47
00:03:10,522 --> 00:03:11,801
all the nutrition went to her brain.

48
00:03:14,321 --> 00:03:15,921
Concentrated is the essence.

49
00:03:16,162 --> 00:03:17,361
All the growth went to the brain.

50
00:03:17,601 --> 00:03:18,881
I grow up becoming hot-tempered.

51
00:03:22,282 --> 00:03:23,081
Thank you to both of you.

52
00:03:25,442 --> 00:03:26,201
What are you saying?

53
00:03:28,402 --> 00:03:29,321
I mean, I'm tired.

54
00:03:29,481 --> 00:03:30,682
I'm going to sleep.

55
00:03:32,282 --> 00:03:33,682
Let's sleep. I'm tired too.

56
00:04:27,241 --> 00:04:27,882
Hello, Mum.

57
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:28,722
What's up?

58
00:04:29,241 --> 00:04:31,082
Xiang Qian, Xiang Qian!

59
00:04:31,801 --> 00:04:33,322
The kitchen knife
in our home is missing.

60
00:04:33,561 --> 00:04:34,282
The kitchen knife is missing?

61
00:04:34,322 --> 00:04:35,361
What do you mean?

62
00:04:36,202 --> 00:04:37,162
Your dad is missing.

63
00:04:37,722 --> 00:04:38,921
I've looked for him everywhere,

64
00:04:39,241 --> 00:04:41,522
and the kitchen knife has gone too.

65
00:04:41,681 --> 00:04:43,121
Do you mean my dad left
with the kitchen knife?

66
00:04:43,962 --> 00:04:46,681
Could he be going after Jiang Hongbin?

67
00:04:48,842 --> 00:04:49,522
Don't panic.

68
00:04:49,642 --> 00:04:50,882
I'll look for him.

69
00:05:24,202 --> 00:05:25,162
Dad, have some tea.

70
00:05:25,882 --> 00:05:26,962
Don't call me Dad.

71
00:05:28,361 --> 00:05:29,962
But, in terms of the relationship,
you are my dad.

72
00:05:32,642 --> 00:05:33,882
Do you still see me as your dad?

73
00:05:35,681 --> 00:05:37,842
Do you still see Xiang Nan as your wife?

74
00:05:40,322 --> 00:05:41,001
Jiang Hongbin,

75
00:05:41,522 --> 00:05:43,241
I entrusted my daughter to you,

76
00:05:44,361 --> 00:05:46,041
but you bullied her!

77
00:05:47,882 --> 00:05:48,322
Dad.

78
00:05:48,361 --> 00:05:49,282
Don't call me Dad.

79
00:05:53,801 --> 00:05:54,801
It's just a minor marital issue

80
00:05:55,241 --> 00:05:57,921
between Xiang Nan and me.

81
00:05:58,322 --> 00:05:59,402
This is very normal.

82
00:06:00,082 --> 00:06:01,481
There's no need to blow it
out of proportion.

83
00:06:01,561 --> 00:06:02,762
Blow it out of proportion?

84
00:06:04,402 --> 00:06:05,322
Do you think
the relationship between you two

85
00:06:05,402 --> 00:06:06,082
is normal?

86
00:06:06,522 --> 00:06:07,441
Before Xiang Nan married,

87
00:06:07,481 --> 00:06:08,282
I've never laid a finger

88
00:06:08,361 --> 00:06:09,202
on her.

89
00:06:09,322 --> 00:06:10,322
I can't bear to do that.

90
00:06:10,681 --> 00:06:11,522
But you?

91
00:06:12,481 --> 00:06:13,361
How dare you treat her

92
00:06:13,402 --> 00:06:14,481
such badly!

93
00:06:14,642 --> 00:06:15,601
Are you even human?

94
00:06:19,202 --> 00:06:20,681
Dad, that's not fair.

95
00:06:21,962 --> 00:06:22,842
It was reported to the police,

96
00:06:23,642 --> 00:06:24,681
and I went to the police station.

97
00:06:25,121 --> 00:06:25,921
Even the police said

98
00:06:25,921 --> 00:06:27,322
it's just a common family dispute.

99
00:06:27,561 --> 00:06:28,601
What more do you want?

100
00:06:29,241 --> 00:06:30,681
Why do you have
to keep holding on to that?

101
00:06:32,681 --> 00:06:33,481
Not to be rude,

102
00:06:33,882 --> 00:06:34,801
but Xiang Nan's

103
00:06:34,962 --> 00:06:36,361
bad habits

104
00:06:36,722 --> 00:06:38,082
are all because you spoiled her.

105
00:06:42,322 --> 00:06:43,041
You animal!

106
00:06:44,441 --> 00:06:45,082
Fine,

107
00:06:46,282 --> 00:06:47,522
you vented.

108
00:06:47,962 --> 00:06:48,842
We're even now.

109
00:06:49,681 --> 00:06:50,601
I call you Dad

110
00:06:51,001 --> 00:06:52,041
because you are an elder to me.

111
00:06:52,561 --> 00:06:53,642
But, don't go overboard.

112
00:06:54,962 --> 00:06:55,762
Listen up!

113
00:06:56,202 --> 00:06:56,842
Jiang Hongbin!

114
00:06:57,561 --> 00:06:58,722
I'm here today

115
00:07:00,202 --> 00:07:01,561
for two reasons.

116
00:07:01,962 --> 00:07:02,681
First,

117
00:07:03,202 --> 00:07:04,601
divorce Xiang Nan immediately!

118
00:07:05,322 --> 00:07:06,041
Second,

119
00:07:06,762 --> 00:07:07,722
for your violence against her,

120
00:07:08,322 --> 00:07:09,402
you must turn yourself in.

121
00:07:11,162 --> 00:07:11,921
Sorry to disappoint you.

122
00:07:12,722 --> 00:07:13,322
First,

123
00:07:13,921 --> 00:07:15,121
I won't divorce her.

124
00:07:15,601 --> 00:07:16,082
Second,

125
00:07:16,282 --> 00:07:18,282
this is normal married life,

126
00:07:18,561 --> 00:07:19,522
not a crime.

127
00:07:19,962 --> 00:07:21,402
So, I don't need to turn myself in.

128
00:07:21,762 --> 00:07:22,962
Don't make a joke with me.

129
00:07:38,681 --> 00:07:40,322
Do you think I'm joking with you?

130
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:41,762
Jiang Hongbin,

131
00:07:43,121 --> 00:07:44,361
I know you're powerful.

132
00:07:45,601 --> 00:07:47,041
Let's settle this between us then.

133
00:07:59,202 --> 00:07:59,921
Come on!

134
00:08:04,842 --> 00:08:06,522
You die or I live?

135
00:08:07,441 --> 00:08:08,202
Come on!

136
00:08:20,322 --> 00:08:20,921
Come on!

137
00:08:20,921 --> 00:08:21,681
Miss Xiang!

138
00:08:21,681 --> 00:08:22,801
Miss Xiang, you can't go in!

139
00:08:23,082 --> 00:08:23,722
Dad!

140
00:08:24,962 --> 00:08:25,921
What are you doing?

141
00:08:27,361 --> 00:08:28,082
This is a company.

142
00:08:28,282 --> 00:08:28,921
There are

143
00:08:29,041 --> 00:08:29,842
surveillance cameras everywhere.

144
00:08:31,241 --> 00:08:32,121
Calm down.

145
00:08:33,121 --> 00:08:34,041
I'll settle this myself.

146
00:08:35,322 --> 00:08:36,402
Let me settle this.

147
00:08:37,242 --> 00:08:37,762
Go down.

148
00:08:38,321 --> 00:08:39,162
Go downstairs and wait for me.

149
00:08:53,081 --> 00:08:54,321
You're always good at
handling things, my sister-in-law.

150
00:08:55,921 --> 00:08:57,242
Dad is just too aggressive!

151
00:09:02,201 --> 00:09:03,041
Jiang Hongbin,

152
00:09:04,321 --> 00:09:05,561
your family is big and prosperous.

153
00:09:06,201 --> 00:09:08,002
You have power, wealth, and influence.

154
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:11,282
Finding a suitable woman

155
00:09:11,402 --> 00:09:12,041
to keep at home

156
00:09:12,081 --> 00:09:12,762
as your wife

157
00:09:12,841 --> 00:09:13,801
shouldn't be difficult.

158
00:09:15,162 --> 00:09:15,841
Why won't you just

159
00:09:15,841 --> 00:09:16,961
let Xiang Nan go leniently?

160
00:09:18,122 --> 00:09:18,841
Why do you escalate this

161
00:09:18,882 --> 00:09:20,122
to legal action?

162
00:09:20,561 --> 00:09:21,162
My dear sister-in-law,

163
00:09:21,762 --> 00:09:23,402
let's leave the topic
about Xiang Nan aside for now.

164
00:09:24,441 --> 00:09:25,801
I need to discuss
something else with you.

165
00:09:26,642 --> 00:09:27,561
Does Chai Jin know

166
00:09:28,122 --> 00:09:29,201
you're here?

167
00:09:31,441 --> 00:09:32,242
Why does he need to know

168
00:09:32,282 --> 00:09:33,721
that I come here?

169
00:09:35,602 --> 00:09:36,441
Apparently, there are some things

170
00:09:36,522 --> 00:09:37,921
you're unaware of.

171
00:09:39,522 --> 00:09:40,402
Maybe

172
00:09:41,081 --> 00:09:42,681
you should ask Chai Jin

173
00:09:43,362 --> 00:09:44,242
if he has done anything

174
00:09:44,602 --> 00:09:45,242
that cannot be told

175
00:09:45,242 --> 00:09:46,402
behind your back.

176
00:09:47,561 --> 00:09:48,441
We're family.

177
00:09:48,841 --> 00:09:50,041
I'm just giving you a heads-up.

178
00:09:50,961 --> 00:09:51,841
If anything happens

179
00:09:51,882 --> 00:09:52,961
to Chai Jin,

180
00:09:53,961 --> 00:09:55,441
your loss could be massive.

181
00:10:01,081 --> 00:10:02,362
I'm not a businessperson.

182
00:10:03,642 --> 00:10:04,522
Business matters

183
00:10:04,561 --> 00:10:05,801
are not important to me now.

184
00:10:06,681 --> 00:10:07,762
As for our family,

185
00:10:07,762 --> 00:10:08,762
the top priority

186
00:10:09,282 --> 00:10:10,362
is Xiang Nan's matter.

187
00:10:14,321 --> 00:10:15,162
Take care, my sister-in-law.

188
00:10:23,961 --> 00:10:24,921
Xiang Qian. Xiang Qian.

189
00:10:25,321 --> 00:10:26,122
How did it go?

190
00:10:26,762 --> 00:10:27,642
Dad, you go home first.

191
00:10:28,002 --> 00:10:29,122
I'm asking you how your
conversation with him went.

192
00:10:29,321 --> 00:10:30,002
When will they divorce?

193
00:10:30,002 --> 00:10:31,321
When will he turn himself in?

194
00:10:31,561 --> 00:10:32,561
Dad, please go home first.

195
00:10:32,681 --> 00:10:33,681
I have to get to the office now.

196
00:10:33,882 --> 00:10:34,441
Why do you go to the office

197
00:10:34,522 --> 00:10:36,321
at a crucial time like this?

198
00:10:36,522 --> 00:10:37,242
I'm going...

199
00:10:37,402 --> 00:10:38,441
I'm going to meet
Chai Jin in the office.

200
00:10:38,721 --> 00:10:39,441
Why do you have

201
00:10:39,642 --> 00:10:40,482
to meet Chai Jin now?

202
00:10:41,762 --> 00:10:42,362
Oh, I got it.

203
00:10:42,522 --> 00:10:43,961
Chai Jin might have some ideas.

204
00:10:44,041 --> 00:10:44,681
This is great.

205
00:10:45,081 --> 00:10:45,921
He'll have a solution.

206
00:10:46,561 --> 00:10:46,921
Dad,

207
00:10:47,122 --> 00:10:49,282
just head home and wait for me

208
00:10:50,362 --> 00:10:51,441
to settle this matter, okay?

209
00:10:51,441 --> 00:10:52,081
Mum is waiting for you at home.

210
00:10:52,081 --> 00:10:52,762
I've called a car for you.

211
00:10:52,961 --> 00:10:54,122
Don't let me leave.

212
00:10:54,602 --> 00:10:55,201
I...

213
00:10:57,362 --> 00:10:58,362
Morning, Ms. Xiang.

214
00:11:06,561 --> 00:11:07,201
Come in.

215
00:11:13,721 --> 00:11:14,321
What's wrong?

216
00:11:14,482 --> 00:11:15,402
Is there anything happened?

217
00:11:15,642 --> 00:11:16,482
Why do you look so serious?

218
00:11:17,522 --> 00:11:18,201
Do you want some coffee?

219
00:11:18,482 --> 00:11:19,201
No.

220
00:11:21,362 --> 00:11:22,602
Do you have any secret deal

221
00:11:22,602 --> 00:11:23,882
with Jiang Hongbin?

222
00:11:27,681 --> 00:11:28,482
What did he say?

223
00:11:31,602 --> 00:11:32,402
He let me ask you.

224
00:11:39,602 --> 00:11:40,522
Does he have any leverage

225
00:11:40,561 --> 00:11:41,441
on you?

226
00:11:42,201 --> 00:11:43,681
What have you two done?

227
00:11:45,882 --> 00:11:47,122
What did he say to you?

228
00:11:47,762 --> 00:11:49,282
He let me ask you.

229
00:11:55,882 --> 00:11:57,402
You're making me anxious.

230
00:12:00,282 --> 00:12:01,081
Why are you keeping silent?

231
00:12:01,081 --> 00:12:02,242
Is it something very serious?

232
00:12:09,321 --> 00:12:10,522
He...

233
00:12:11,762 --> 00:12:12,762
He has

234
00:12:13,321 --> 00:12:14,402
a stake in a company

235
00:12:14,762 --> 00:12:15,642
that aims to obtain

236
00:12:16,282 --> 00:12:17,602
the gas pipeline

237
00:12:17,841 --> 00:12:18,721
renovation contract.

238
00:12:20,041 --> 00:12:21,242
He asked me to pull some strings

239
00:12:21,282 --> 00:12:22,242
at the Housing and
Urban Development Bureau.

240
00:12:23,441 --> 00:12:24,242
And did you?

241
00:12:25,002 --> 00:12:25,721
I did.

242
00:12:27,282 --> 00:12:28,041
Everything has settled?

243
00:12:29,561 --> 00:12:30,242
I gave out 200,000 yuan.

244
00:12:31,482 --> 00:12:33,441
Why didn't you discuss it with me?

245
00:12:34,122 --> 00:12:35,402
Time was a constraint.

246
00:12:35,482 --> 00:12:36,201
I haven't had time

247
00:12:36,201 --> 00:12:37,242
to report to you yet.

248
00:12:38,122 --> 00:12:38,762
You've really

249
00:12:39,762 --> 00:12:41,282
put me in a difficult position.

250
00:12:42,002 --> 00:12:42,801
Hold on. What happened?

251
00:12:43,081 --> 00:12:44,242
Why would he

252
00:12:44,321 --> 00:12:45,561
suddenly bring this up to you?

253
00:12:45,681 --> 00:12:47,201
Nothing has even started yet.

254
00:12:47,441 --> 00:12:48,841
He wanted to withdraw himself?

255
00:12:49,402 --> 00:12:50,362
Can we pause the collaboration

256
00:12:50,362 --> 00:12:51,522
with Jiang Hongbin for now?

257
00:12:53,041 --> 00:12:53,801
Is that possible?

258
00:12:56,362 --> 00:12:57,602
But, you have to tell me

259
00:12:57,602 --> 00:12:58,841
what is going on.

260
00:12:59,482 --> 00:13:02,002
I need to check on a few things first,

261
00:13:02,321 --> 00:13:03,961
and settle something

262
00:13:04,482 --> 00:13:05,642
before I explain everything to you.

263
00:13:19,642 --> 00:13:20,362
Sorry.

264
00:13:20,801 --> 00:13:23,242
The person you call is unavailable.

265
00:13:28,561 --> 00:13:29,162
Xiang Zhong,

266
00:13:30,282 --> 00:13:31,242
is there anything

267
00:13:31,321 --> 00:13:32,801
happens in your family?

268
00:13:43,841 --> 00:13:44,961
Please have your seat first.

269
00:13:47,402 --> 00:13:48,162
Please wait a moment.

270
00:13:48,321 --> 00:13:49,642
I'll get back to you in half an hour.

271
00:13:52,402 --> 00:13:53,482
(Law Firm)
I'm sorry.

272
00:13:53,602 --> 00:13:54,602
A client came in unexpectedly.

273
00:13:55,362 --> 00:13:56,041
I apologize

274
00:13:56,201 --> 00:13:57,321
for bothering you lately.

275
00:13:57,602 --> 00:13:58,162
It's my job.

276
00:13:58,282 --> 00:13:58,921
What can I help you with?

277
00:14:00,921 --> 00:14:02,841
I want to consult you.

278
00:14:03,162 --> 00:14:04,441
If someone bribes

279
00:14:04,642 --> 00:14:05,961
a government official,

280
00:14:06,122 --> 00:14:07,081
how will the sentence be determined?

281
00:14:07,882 --> 00:14:08,841
How much was involved?

282
00:14:09,801 --> 00:14:11,321
Around 200,000 yuan.

283
00:14:12,561 --> 00:14:13,841
If there's clear evidence,

284
00:14:14,002 --> 00:14:15,162
the sentence should be
no more than three years.

285
00:14:15,602 --> 00:14:16,081
However,

286
00:14:16,282 --> 00:14:17,321
with a good confession,

287
00:14:17,801 --> 00:14:19,041
the sentence

288
00:14:19,122 --> 00:14:20,122
may be reduced accordingly.

289
00:14:36,482 --> 00:14:37,041
Dad!

290
00:14:38,242 --> 00:14:39,721
Why didn't you go home?

291
00:14:40,482 --> 00:14:41,162
Oh!

292
00:14:41,362 --> 00:14:42,482
I made this

293
00:14:42,801 --> 00:14:43,561
for you.

294
00:14:44,201 --> 00:14:46,041
Your favorite stir-fried eels

295
00:14:46,441 --> 00:14:47,201
and water-shield soup.

296
00:14:47,961 --> 00:14:48,841
That's great

297
00:14:48,961 --> 00:14:49,642
that you're back!

298
00:14:52,522 --> 00:14:53,282
Where's Xiang Nan?

299
00:14:53,762 --> 00:14:54,402
Xiang Nan?

300
00:14:54,482 --> 00:14:55,841
Xiang Zhong took her downstairs

301
00:14:55,921 --> 00:14:57,602
to the convenience store.

302
00:14:59,201 --> 00:14:59,921
Great.

303
00:15:00,122 --> 00:15:00,721
After

304
00:15:01,362 --> 00:15:01,882
having the meal,

305
00:15:01,882 --> 00:15:03,201
you should go get some rest too.

306
00:15:07,522 --> 00:15:08,321
You must be tired.

307
00:15:10,882 --> 00:15:11,681
Eat more.

308
00:15:16,441 --> 00:15:17,081
Look,

309
00:15:18,642 --> 00:15:19,882
back then,

310
00:15:21,081 --> 00:15:21,841
this amount of rice

311
00:15:22,441 --> 00:15:23,482
was just enough

312
00:15:23,642 --> 00:15:24,441
for Xiang Nan.

313
00:15:25,441 --> 00:15:26,242
But now,

314
00:15:26,801 --> 00:15:28,482
she's barely touched it.

315
00:15:30,762 --> 00:15:31,561
Xiang Qian,

316
00:15:33,282 --> 00:15:34,201
we can't keep leaving

317
00:15:34,242 --> 00:15:35,602
Xiang Nan's matter unresolved.

318
00:15:36,642 --> 00:15:37,561
As long as this is not settled,

319
00:15:38,561 --> 00:15:40,242
I can't be at ease.

320
00:15:40,882 --> 00:15:42,402
Xiang Nan will suffer too.

321
00:15:42,841 --> 00:15:44,041
She was always thin,

322
00:15:44,602 --> 00:15:46,282
and she's getting even thinner.

323
00:15:48,921 --> 00:15:49,522
I know.

324
00:15:51,482 --> 00:15:52,921
As the eldest daughter

325
00:15:54,321 --> 00:15:55,201
and the eldest sister,

326
00:15:56,162 --> 00:15:57,762
you have to protect your sister.

327
00:16:04,441 --> 00:16:06,441
I need to clear

328
00:16:07,841 --> 00:16:09,002
some things up first for now.

329
00:16:09,762 --> 00:16:10,961
Only then

330
00:16:11,081 --> 00:16:13,882
I can figure out the best way

331
00:16:14,441 --> 00:16:16,321
to help Xiang Nan

332
00:16:16,602 --> 00:16:18,002
with her divorce.

333
00:16:18,681 --> 00:16:19,242
Okay?

334
00:16:19,882 --> 00:16:20,681
I'll do it as soon as possible.

335
00:16:29,921 --> 00:16:30,882
Sorry for making you trouble.

336
00:16:33,122 --> 00:16:33,961
Eat well.

337
00:17:08,081 --> 00:17:09,081
(Xiang Zhong: How's it going?)

338
00:17:10,082 --> 00:17:11,882
(Xiang Qian: It's complicated
as it involves Chai Jin now.)

339
00:17:16,481 --> 00:17:17,842
(Give me some time to figure it out.)

340
00:17:21,642 --> 00:17:23,042
(Xiang Zhong: Contact me
anytime if needed.)

341
00:17:30,201 --> 00:17:30,882
Qian Feng!

342
00:17:32,961 --> 00:17:33,481
Mrs. Deng.

343
00:17:33,802 --> 00:17:34,241
Xiang...

344
00:17:34,521 --> 00:17:35,362
Why are you here?

345
00:17:36,362 --> 00:17:38,602
I wanted to tell you over the phone,

346
00:17:38,802 --> 00:17:40,082
but after thinking it over,

347
00:17:40,521 --> 00:17:42,402
I think it would be better
to tell you in person.

348
00:17:42,882 --> 00:17:44,162
What's going on? Come over here.

349
00:17:47,681 --> 00:17:49,281
Haiyang's mother's condition
hasn't improved.

350
00:17:50,122 --> 00:17:51,521
She's in a wheelchair now,

351
00:17:52,761 --> 00:17:55,241
and she doesn't really
recognize people now.

352
00:17:55,602 --> 00:17:57,441
Her personality became a bit

353
00:17:58,001 --> 00:17:58,721
weird.

354
00:18:00,521 --> 00:18:01,201
Mrs. Deng,

355
00:18:02,642 --> 00:18:04,162
Haiyang

356
00:18:05,241 --> 00:18:06,602
is ready

357
00:18:07,322 --> 00:18:09,241
to start over a new life with you.

358
00:18:09,348 --> 00:18:10,956
He's reviewed

359
00:18:10,982 --> 00:18:12,157
the messages you sent

360
00:18:12,159 --> 00:18:13,236
multiple times.

361
00:18:13,562 --> 00:18:14,761
He even found a job

362
00:18:14,802 --> 00:18:15,481
in Shanghai

363
00:18:15,481 --> 00:18:16,961
with a 500,000 yuan annual salary.

364
00:18:17,362 --> 00:18:19,322
He knows you love Shanghai.

365
00:18:20,162 --> 00:18:21,042
So, he tried his best

366
00:18:21,042 --> 00:18:22,241
to make a home for you

367
00:18:22,281 --> 00:18:23,362
in Shanghai.

368
00:18:23,642 --> 00:18:25,362
Even though he couldn't
afford a home by now,

369
00:18:26,122 --> 00:18:27,082
he said he would

370
00:18:27,162 --> 00:18:28,642
rent a decent home for you.

371
00:18:29,402 --> 00:18:30,162
But then,

372
00:18:32,281 --> 00:18:33,322
no one expects

373
00:18:34,241 --> 00:18:36,001
that his mother falls ill
at this very moment.

374
00:18:36,761 --> 00:18:37,481
Hold on, Qian Feng.

375
00:18:37,562 --> 00:18:38,721
None of this means

376
00:18:38,921 --> 00:18:39,721
anything to me anymore.

377
00:18:39,802 --> 00:18:40,562
Can you understand?

378
00:18:41,162 --> 00:18:42,241
I have to let you know.

379
00:18:46,082 --> 00:18:46,921
Haiyang made you angry deliberately

380
00:18:47,001 --> 00:18:48,001
to make you leave.

381
00:18:49,921 --> 00:18:50,602
He didn't want you

382
00:18:50,642 --> 00:18:52,201
to take care of his mother with him.

383
00:18:52,761 --> 00:18:54,042
He also didn't want

384
00:18:54,362 --> 00:18:56,042
to let you bear such a heavy burden.

385
00:18:56,921 --> 00:18:58,082
He said this is just

386
00:18:58,162 --> 00:18:59,201
too unfair to you.

387
00:19:00,402 --> 00:19:01,602
He is sincere

388
00:19:01,642 --> 00:19:03,201
and wanted to make up with you.

389
00:19:04,362 --> 00:19:05,921
But, things didn't go as planned.

390
00:19:07,402 --> 00:19:08,402
Seeing my brother like that

391
00:19:10,362 --> 00:19:12,082
all these while

392
00:19:13,322 --> 00:19:14,521
really upsets me.

393
00:19:16,602 --> 00:19:17,241
Mrs. Deng,

394
00:19:18,602 --> 00:19:19,961
he must be

395
00:19:20,921 --> 00:19:21,882
in great distress now.

396
00:19:24,521 --> 00:19:26,001
He forced you away

397
00:19:27,042 --> 00:19:28,441
out of his love for you.

398
00:19:46,201 --> 00:19:47,802
What are you doing here?

399
00:19:49,602 --> 00:19:50,921
I'm waiting for you.

400
00:19:52,481 --> 00:19:53,642
Didn't you say yesterday

401
00:19:54,642 --> 00:19:56,241
you'd explain why

402
00:19:57,562 --> 00:19:58,642
