403
00:19:58,681 --> 00:19:59,362
with Jiang Hongbin?

404
00:20:00,761 --> 00:20:02,162
Xiang Nan wants a divorce from him.

405
00:20:05,441 --> 00:20:06,281
What happened?

406
00:20:08,681 --> 00:20:10,001
Does Jiang Hongbin have

407
00:20:10,281 --> 00:20:11,042
an affair outside?

408
00:20:14,761 --> 00:20:15,802
Then, that's domestic violence.

409
00:20:17,602 --> 00:20:19,082
A form of it,

410
00:20:19,602 --> 00:20:20,921
but worse.

411
00:20:22,162 --> 00:20:23,721
There's a term for it nowadays,

412
00:20:23,802 --> 00:20:24,842
marital rape.

413
00:20:27,281 --> 00:20:28,402
Even without that,

414
00:20:28,802 --> 00:20:29,562
Xiang Nan won't

415
00:20:29,562 --> 00:20:30,681
stay with him until the end.

416
00:20:31,562 --> 00:20:32,602
The initial purpose of Jiang Hongbin

417
00:20:32,602 --> 00:20:33,761
marrying Xiang Nan

418
00:20:33,961 --> 00:20:35,681
was to keep her

419
00:20:35,961 --> 00:20:37,122
at home

420
00:20:37,201 --> 00:20:38,681
as his obedient wife,

421
00:20:39,322 --> 00:20:40,642
playing the role of Mrs. Jiang,

422
00:20:41,441 --> 00:20:42,281
accompanying him to events,

423
00:20:42,362 --> 00:20:43,802
and doing whatever he requested.

424
00:20:44,921 --> 00:20:45,921
But, how could it be possible?

425
00:20:46,001 --> 00:20:47,241
Xiang Nan is an artistic person

426
00:20:47,322 --> 00:20:49,281
who pursues freedom.

427
00:20:51,122 --> 00:20:52,481
At the beginning

428
00:20:52,681 --> 00:20:53,481
of their marriage,

429
00:20:53,961 --> 00:20:55,082
he was subtle,

430
00:20:55,602 --> 00:20:56,721
and even supportive of Xiang Nan

431
00:20:56,842 --> 00:20:57,842
going out to work.

432
00:20:58,162 --> 00:20:58,882
But, behind her back,

433
00:20:58,921 --> 00:21:00,082
he plays a lot of tricks

434
00:21:00,201 --> 00:21:01,521
to force Xiang Nan home.

435
00:21:02,882 --> 00:21:04,201
He's been shady.

436
00:21:05,481 --> 00:21:07,001
Maybe he couldn't tolerate it anymore.

437
00:21:07,521 --> 00:21:09,402
So, he revealed his true colors

438
00:21:09,842 --> 00:21:10,882
and started getting physical.

439
00:21:11,802 --> 00:21:12,521
I understand now.

440
00:21:14,642 --> 00:21:15,642
So, what did he say?

441
00:21:16,961 --> 00:21:19,001
I went to his company yesterday

442
00:21:19,001 --> 00:21:20,122
because of Xiang Nan's matter.

443
00:21:20,602 --> 00:21:21,602
It ended up that he asked me

444
00:21:22,562 --> 00:21:23,882
to come back asking you about that.

445
00:21:24,882 --> 00:21:26,281
It comes to my senses later.

446
00:21:26,882 --> 00:21:28,281
If Xiang Nan insists

447
00:21:28,322 --> 00:21:29,602
on a divorce,

448
00:21:30,602 --> 00:21:32,642
he's going to report you.

449
00:21:35,921 --> 00:21:37,681
Let him go ahead.

450
00:21:40,148 --> 00:21:40,909
Boss,

451
00:21:42,281 --> 00:21:43,001
the person you bribed

452
00:21:43,042 --> 00:21:44,481
is a government official.

453
00:21:45,241 --> 00:21:46,162
I consulted

454
00:21:46,201 --> 00:21:46,882
Attorney Wu regarding this already.

455
00:21:47,481 --> 00:21:48,802
If the evidence is solid,

456
00:21:48,842 --> 00:21:50,322
the sentence will be no more than
three years for a 200,000 yuan bribe.

457
00:21:51,082 --> 00:21:52,481
With a good attitude,

458
00:21:53,602 --> 00:21:54,761
it may be less.

459
00:21:56,362 --> 00:21:58,082
Even without Xiang Nan's matter,

460
00:21:58,481 --> 00:21:59,921
there's something amiss about our
collaboration with Jiang Hongbin.

461
00:22:00,281 --> 00:22:02,082
He has plenty of social resources,

462
00:22:02,122 --> 00:22:04,362
but why did he
make you manage the things?

463
00:22:04,921 --> 00:22:05,842
Isn't it obvious

464
00:22:05,842 --> 00:22:07,082
he's setting you up?

465
00:22:07,241 --> 00:22:08,721
Even a fool knows this.

466
00:22:09,042 --> 00:22:10,761
Then, why did you still do that?

467
00:22:11,082 --> 00:22:12,602
If I don't, how is that possible for us

468
00:22:12,602 --> 00:22:14,042
to obtain those two big projects?

469
00:22:15,362 --> 00:22:16,562
You know that the two projects

470
00:22:16,642 --> 00:22:17,961
are crucial

471
00:22:18,042 --> 00:22:18,882
for our new company.

472
00:22:19,001 --> 00:22:19,362
Am I right?

473
00:22:19,402 --> 00:22:20,001
Besides, this includes

474
00:22:20,042 --> 00:22:21,082
your favorite

475
00:22:21,162 --> 00:22:22,402
elderly care sector.

476
00:22:23,122 --> 00:22:24,042
So I thought,

477
00:22:24,602 --> 00:22:25,721
even if it's risky,

478
00:22:25,802 --> 00:22:27,162
it's worth the shot.

479
00:22:28,001 --> 00:22:28,842
Plus,

480
00:22:29,521 --> 00:22:31,642
Jiang Hongbin is your brother-in-law.

481
00:22:32,441 --> 00:22:33,001
I thought it would be fine

482
00:22:33,162 --> 00:22:34,802
as you're a family.

483
00:22:36,602 --> 00:22:38,562
Who would've thought
that he'd be this wicked?

484
00:22:44,441 --> 00:22:45,201
Alright.

485
00:22:46,281 --> 00:22:47,642
Since it's come to this,

486
00:22:48,521 --> 00:22:49,441
there's no point dwelling on it.

487
00:22:49,842 --> 00:22:50,521
You

488
00:22:51,642 --> 00:22:53,001
should relax for now,

489
00:22:53,281 --> 00:22:54,122
and don't think too much of it.

490
00:22:58,201 --> 00:22:58,921
Relax.

491
00:23:00,322 --> 00:23:01,761
If Jiang Hongbin

492
00:23:03,042 --> 00:23:04,402
takes this

493
00:23:04,402 --> 00:23:05,441
to blackmail us,

494
00:23:06,441 --> 00:23:07,681
we won't back down.

495
00:23:08,241 --> 00:23:09,241
Let's go against him.

496
00:23:10,082 --> 00:23:11,402
After all, he's a wise businessperson.

497
00:23:11,562 --> 00:23:12,122
Right?

498
00:23:12,642 --> 00:23:13,402
For this matter,

499
00:23:13,521 --> 00:23:15,082
he'll weigh his options,

500
00:23:15,681 --> 00:23:16,602
and if he goes through with it,

501
00:23:16,681 --> 00:23:18,402
he stands to lose much more than we do.

502
00:23:19,402 --> 00:23:20,042
Am I right?

503
00:23:20,521 --> 00:23:22,162
How can there not be any pressure?

504
00:24:02,001 --> 00:24:02,521
Here.

505
00:24:03,921 --> 00:24:04,562
Okay.

506
00:24:04,761 --> 00:24:05,441
Deng Haiyang.

507
00:24:06,961 --> 00:24:07,882
What happened?

508
00:24:09,241 --> 00:24:10,602
My mum won't let me touch her now.

509
00:24:10,721 --> 00:24:11,882
