clean clothes on her?

514
00:24:23,362 --> 00:24:24,042
I...

515
00:24:24,162 --> 00:24:25,642
I wanted to clean for her, but...

516
00:24:29,802 --> 00:24:30,842
Fine, get a basin of warm water

517
00:24:31,281 --> 00:24:32,842
and bring her some clean clothes.

518
00:24:34,921 --> 00:24:35,481
Alright.

519
00:24:43,162 --> 00:24:44,322
Do you recognize me?

520
00:24:48,441 --> 00:24:49,322
Don't be afraid.

521
00:24:49,441 --> 00:24:50,201
Later,

522
00:24:50,521 --> 00:24:52,201
let's wipe you down

523
00:24:52,241 --> 00:24:53,122
and change into clean clothes,

524
00:24:53,122 --> 00:24:54,241
so you'll feel more comfortable.

525
00:24:56,562 --> 00:24:57,362
Keep your feet covered,

526
00:24:57,521 --> 00:24:58,281
so you don't catch a cold.

527
00:25:05,562 --> 00:25:06,402
Be good. Everything will be fine.

528
00:25:07,721 --> 00:25:08,402
Give it to me.

529
00:25:08,721 --> 00:25:09,281
Here you go.

530
00:25:13,961 --> 00:25:14,602
Stay aside

531
00:25:14,802 --> 00:25:15,921
and wait me out there.

532
00:25:16,082 --> 00:25:16,521
Alright.

533
00:25:16,521 --> 00:25:17,322
I'll call you when I'm done.

534
00:25:27,122 --> 00:25:27,802
Deng Haiyang,

535
00:25:28,001 --> 00:25:28,602
this towel

536
00:25:28,602 --> 00:25:29,521
is too rough.

537
00:25:30,122 --> 00:25:31,362
I'll bring a couple from home next time.

538
00:25:36,562 --> 00:25:38,122
Let's clean you up, okay?

539
00:25:39,481 --> 00:25:40,441
Don't be afraid.

540
00:25:41,322 --> 00:25:42,921
You're such a neat lady.

541
00:25:43,761 --> 00:25:44,642
You should keep

542
00:25:44,802 --> 00:25:45,921
clean and neat

543
00:25:46,281 --> 00:25:47,562
to look presentable, right?

544
00:26:08,001 --> 00:26:08,761
Is she your wife?

545
00:26:09,122 --> 00:26:09,961
She's so nice.

546
00:26:13,642 --> 00:26:14,322
Ex-wife.

547
00:26:14,721 --> 00:26:15,562
Ex-wife.

548
00:26:17,001 --> 00:26:17,921
She's such a great woman.

549
00:26:18,042 --> 00:26:19,122
Hurry up and win her back.

550
00:26:21,681 --> 00:26:23,201
It's not appropriate
to discuss others like this!

551
00:26:32,122 --> 00:26:32,562
Here,

552
00:26:34,122 --> 00:26:34,761
arm up.

553
00:26:36,122 --> 00:26:37,322
Let's get you into

554
00:26:40,402 --> 00:26:41,761
clean clothes

555
00:26:42,042 --> 00:26:43,322
and you'll feel better.

556
00:26:44,362 --> 00:26:45,201
Here, put your arm in.

557
00:26:45,761 --> 00:26:46,681
That's right. This arm.

558
00:26:47,441 --> 00:26:48,122
The sleeve is here.

559
00:26:48,961 --> 00:26:49,882
Yeah, put your arm in.

560
00:26:51,362 --> 00:26:52,241
That's great!

561
00:26:53,042 --> 00:26:53,921
You'll feel better now.

562
00:26:54,082 --> 00:26:54,642
Right?

563
00:26:56,802 --> 00:26:57,481
She's done changing the clothes.

564
00:28:00,842 --> 00:28:02,162
