567
00:28:06,961 --> 00:28:07,961
She can't stop my mum

568
00:28:08,201 --> 00:28:09,162
from smashing things every day.

569
00:28:10,481 --> 00:28:11,322
- That's true.
- Then, she can't handle this.

570
00:28:12,802 --> 00:28:14,162
She's had a strong
personality all her life.

571
00:28:14,247 --> 00:28:15,447
Anyone would find this hard.

572
00:28:17,761 --> 00:28:18,842
And, next time,

573
00:28:18,961 --> 00:28:20,042
you can just tell me the real situation.

574
00:28:20,162 --> 00:28:21,122
I'll decide on my own

575
00:28:21,122 --> 00:28:21,842
whether I want to come or not.

576
00:28:26,721 --> 00:28:27,281
I'm here today

577
00:28:27,281 --> 00:28:28,521
helping your mum change her clothes

578
00:28:28,562 --> 00:28:29,281
doesn't mean I'm here

579
